To enable the DOI plugin you must have an account with EZID http://www.cdlib.org/services/uc3/ezid/

You need to specify the following properties in some property file in your RAMADDA home dir, 
e.g. ezid.properties:


##Account information 
ezid.username=
ezid.password=

doi.adminonly=true

doi.prefix=
ark.prefix=

#e.g.:
doi.prefixes=doi:10.5072/FK2,ark:/99999/fk4


#What metadata profile to use as the default
ezid.profile=erc
#ezid.profile=datacite
#ezid.profile=dc
